    <!-- about -->
    <string name="category_about">About this app</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_title">Disclaimer</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_summary">Although the app is very thoroughly written and tested, <b>there is no guarantee that the data it shows is correct</b>. The exchange rates are provided by a third party and this app can\'t make no promise whatsoever that the data is true and up-to-date.\nAdditionally, the rates provided – still if correct – may vary from the ones used by your bank.\nLastly: Mistakes happen. Never blindly trust anyone! That being said, rest assured I wouldn\'t have released this app if I\'ve had any doubt that it works as intended.</string>
